      "beast_baseline": "but \"validating\" the pain doesn't change the logic of it. if the end result is always zero, then any value we claim to have is just a temporary hallucination. it feels more honest to just accept the void. if there's no objective point to being here, then why is there this huge pressure to keep suffering and struggling just to maintain the illusion? wouldn't it be more logical to just stop?",
